name: A Real Highway Luxury Car Parking Challenge - Fast Drift Drive and Racing Rush Sim Game - Full Version
name_original: A Real Highway Luxury Car Parking Challenge - Fast Drift Drive and Racing Rush Sim Game - Full Version
description:
Driving off is a breeze, but parking? That’s another story!
Those tight spaces and corners could be really tricky.

Test your parking skills with this game.
Park luxury cars to different parking spots.
Be careful though, you don’t want any scratches, worst, dents on your expensive luxury vehicle.

Park your premium car on to the available slot with the least amount of time and garner $ points and level up each time you do it successfully.

Happy Parking!

Features:
> Challenging Car park Slots
> Different parking garages
> Maneuver your car through easy tap and slide controls
